modules.description: This module provides functions for traversing directory trees, searching for files, and copying or creating files and directories. It works with file paths represented as `Fpath.t` values and supports operations like walking directory structures with `walk_down`, searching upward for files with `find_up`, and copying files or directories with customizable name rewriting. Concrete use cases include file system navigation, file creation with `touch_file`, and recursive directory copying with attribute preservation.
